Notes
-----
!window popsup & prints found but not the right password
 ->thats from funzip CRC Match please ingnore
 ->when you get popup (window found) check if CRC error printed out on
   funzip side if not then thats the right password
   else
   just a CRC Match so ignore & also check ZipRecoVer:Recv_Files/
   & delete unwanted files.

!can i download other wordlist files & try them in ziprecover.
 ->Yes (you can also creat your own by liste'm all down & save)


